{"tid":298314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好成日笑廢中廢老，根本而家唔少後生既都好撚乞衣格","createTime":"2017-06-26T07:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T07:56:53.000Z","uid":102994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1475586bbeb8f898c8bfea46a4fdc637848dfc70","tid":298314,"uid":102994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，樓豬而家喺日本去緊旅行 見唔少地方既廁所都會放卷spare廁紙比人用，我就諗起有次去完廁所見個八婆同學拎住一大舊野出廁格<br />\n我: 做咩去完廁所多左野既<br />\n八婆: 哦，我拎廁紙返hall用呀<br />\n我: 下可以拎既咩<br />\n八婆: 咁佢擺得喺度都預左比學生用既，個個都係咁架啦，我住左大半年hall除左第一個月之外一卷廁紙都冇買過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰刻我都唔知講咩好，痴撚線廁紙咁平都唔肯自己買，偷野仲大大聲咁得戚，知唔知醜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算佢擺出黎都係預你去廁所嗰時用架啦，更何況佢本身就收埋左既，唔怪得而家喺學校成日冇廁紙用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲衰撚過d廢中廢老見有試食就拎走大半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}